ing highway 280 north & south exit sand hill road east toward stanford continue east turning right at the traffic light on santa cruz avenue make an immediate left onto junipero serra boulevard turn left at the second stoplight campus drive east continue around campus drive east and turn left when you reach serra street follow serra street until it ends at galvez street turn right onto galvez go two long blocks cross campus drive to the public parking lot by the track upon walking out of the parking lot and turning to your left you will walk two long blocks on galvez before coming to a dead end at serra encina hall is a large stone building at 616 serra street there are parking meters in front of the building fsi stanford is on the first floor of encina hall please note that parking is monitored monday friday 8 am 4 pm additional parking there is additional parking along galvez street next to the stanford track stadium and next to the landau center galvez at memorial way contact information voice 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages campus map printable map of the stanford campus 2.9 mb with parking areas indicated marguerite bus map the marguerite is stanford university's campus shuttle a printable map of the bus routes serving the stanford campus 700kb support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 723 4581 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
